---
title: Double Southeast Asian Crispy Chicken Bowl with Rainbow Slaw & Garlic Aioli
description: You’ve probably had your fair share of chicken and slaw, but this one may come out as the best because of how crispy
the chicken is and how delicious it becomes on top of a ponzu-dressed slaw. What do you think, is chicken and slaw back on the menu?
